<plot>Angel seeks revenge on Pablo, the man who was having an affair with his wife and whom he blames for her death. He finds Pablo hiding hiding from the law in the small town of La Paz, Mexico. When the two meet, Angel questions Pablo about the affair he had with, Ely, his wife. Pablo reveals Ely as a woman who lived two separate lives. Angel discovers things are not what they appeared to be and the woman that these two men loved, lived and loved them her own way. La Paz was written and directed by Felix Martiz.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?305364</url></doc>
